  cons = '{"en":["Creative writing less natural than ChatGPT/Claude","Advanced features need Google One subscription","Privacy concerns for enterprise users","Inconsistent response quality sometimes"],"hi":["क्रिएटिव लेखन ChatGPT/Claude से कम स्वाभाविक","Advanced फीचर्स के लिए Google One सब्सक्रिप्शन","एंटरप्राइज़ यूज़र्स के लिए गोपनीयता चिंताएं","कभी-कभी असंगत जवाब की गुणवत्ता"],"hinglish":["Creative writing ChatGPT/Claude se kam natural","Advanced features ke liye Google One subscription","Enterprise users ke liye privacy concerns","Kabhi kabhi inconsistent response quality"]}',
